docs {
  # Get Project Conversations
  
  Get all chat windows (tmux) for a specific project.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  - `projectId` (string): Base64-encoded project path
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "conversations": [
      {
        "id": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
        "terminalId": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
        "windowName": "chat-claude-auth-bug",
        "tool": "claude",
        "topic": "auth-bug",
        "type": "chat",
        "active": true
      }
    ],
    "total": 1,
    "projectName": "my-project",
    "projectPath": "/Users/user/Code/my-project"
  }
  ```
}
